
@BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

### auth register
POST {{BASE_URL}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

### auth login
POST {{BASE_URL}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

### auth logout
POST {{BASE_URL}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

### auth refresh
POST {{BASE_URL}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
 
### auth me
GET {{BASE_URL}}/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json